videos.description: Jimmy Butler pokes the ball loose from LeBron James then speeds to the other end for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Butler throws down fast-break slam

videos.description: LeBron James goes full extension to block Tyler Herro's layup attempt.

videos.headline: LeBron rises to block Herro

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma gets the ball in the corner and pulls up for a 3-pointer as time expires to cut the Heat's lead to 26-23.
videos.headline: Kuzma drains 3 to end 1st quarter

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma gets the and-1 bucket but he skips high-fiving Anthony Davis on the bench.
videos.headline: Kuzma leaves AD hanging

videos.description: LeBron James hustles on the fast break to smack down Tyler Herro's attempt.

videos.headline: LeBron chases down Herro for another block

videos.description: Rajon Rondo throws the perfect lob to Anthony Davis who throws down the reverse dunk.

videos.headline: Rondo goes up top to Davis for the dunk

videos.description: Chris Paul speaks on the NBA's fight against social injustice and how proud he is of the initiative the league is taking getting people registered to vote.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Paul proud getting 90% of the league registered to vote) 2020/10/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paul proud getting 90% of the league registered to vote

videos.description: Tyler Herro knocks down the 3-pointer over LeBron James forcing the Lakers to call timeout.

videos.headline: Herro drains 3 in LeBron's face

videos.description: Jimmy Butler goes up for the lay-in, but is met by Rajon Rondo who sends him to the ground.

videos.description: Jimmy Butler puts the Heat up 9 with a little over a minute left, then says to his team "Lakers are in trouble."
